title: Thom Hartmann Program - October 01 2013
description:
October 01, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 

Hour One: The GOP strategy for killing Obamacare -  Chairman/Congressman Steve Israel, Democratic Congressional Campaign Committee (DCCC)

Hour Two: Why would African Americans want to disenfranchise black voters?  Cherylyn Harley LeBon, Project 21 National Advisory Board / Plus, Government shutdown...brought to you by Citizens United

Hour Three: The illusion of nuclear safety - Eric Schlosser, Command and Control
